# Claude Hub 开发 Agent Team 配置

## 团队结构

```
Claude Hub 项目开发团队：

- 团队负责人 (Team Lead) - 主会话，协调工作、分配任务
- 前端工程师 (Frontend Engineer) - React 组件、UI 开发
- 后端工程师 (Backend Engineer) - Electron 主进程、IPC、数据持久化
- 测试工程师 (QA Engineer) - 单元测试、集成测试
```

## 使用方法

### 启动团队

在 Claude Code 中运行以下命令：

```
Create an agent team to develop Claude Hub features. Use these teammates:
- Frontend: Focus on React components, UI/UX, user interactions
- Backend: Focus on Electron main process, IPC, data persistence
- QA: Focus on testing, bug verification, quality assurance

Each teammate should work independently and communicate through the team lead.
```

### 或者使用预定义配置

我先创建一个项目级的 Agent 配置文件，方便快速启动：
<minimax:tool_call>
<invoke name="Write">
<parameter name="content">{
  "teamName": "claude-hub-dev",
  "description": "Claude Hub 项目开发团队",
  "teammates": [
    {
      "name": "frontend-engineer",
      "role": "Frontend Engineer",
      "description": "负责 React 组件开发、UI/UX 改进、样式优化",
      "focus": [
        "src/renderer/**/*",
        "组件开发",
        "用户界面",
        "样式与交互"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "backend-engineer",
      "role": "Backend Engineer",
      "description": "负责 Electron 主进程、IPC 通信、数据持久化、系统集成",
      "focus": [
        "src/main/**/*",
        "Electron 主进程",
        "IPC 通信",
        "系统集成"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "qa-engineer",
      "role": "QA Engineer",
      "description": "负责测试、bug 修复验证、代码审查、质量保证",
      "focus": [
        "测试验证",
        "Bug 修复",
        "代码审查",
        "质量保证"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "workflow": {
    "taskAssignment": "lead assigns tasks based on teammate focus areas",
    "communication": "teammates report to lead, can communicate with each other",
    "review": "QA reviews all changes before merge",
    "coordination": "lead coordinates parallel work to avoid conflicts"
  },
  "bestPractices": [
    "每个队友拥有独立的工作文件，避免冲突",
    "负责人将工作分解为清晰的任务单元",
    "队友完成工作后通知负责人进行审查",
    "定期检查进度，重定向不起作用的方法"
  ]
}
